Memorial Day weekend is welcoming sales left and right. During the long weekend, you can land savings on beloved brands such as Wayfair, Best Buy, Sephora, Madewell and more. Top selling categories, such as furniture, fashion and televisions, are also offering can’t-beat deals. Speaking of televisions, Samsung has decided to markdown their best-selling Frame TV for Memorial Day weekend only. Right now, you can land the The Frame QLED 4K Smart TV (2022) for up to $300 off alongside a customizable bezel for 50% off. Not only will you be saving some big bucks, but you can also enjoy billions of bright colors at 100% color volume, more screen visibility with nearly no light reflection, a slim-fit wall mount and, of course, a customizable bezel. With a purchase of a Samsung Frame TV, you’ll additionally have the capability to display personal photos and appreciate creative pieces with the use of Art Mode. Therefore, it won’t only enhance your streaming tendencies but also your home. To take advantage of this limited-time Samsung Frame TV deal, simply choose the 2022 model and select your TV size from the seven various options. Then, opt for a black, modern white or modern brown bezel color. Best of all, you can choose to pay all at once or in separate installments, making the Frame TV accessible to many. For more content, check out the New York Post Shopping section.